		Un-tick this if the channel has a 'wide' logo like TV1000
	</p>
	<p>
	  <%= f.label :encoding %><br />
	  <%= f.select (:encoding, @encodings)   %>
	</p>
	<p>
		<%= f.check_box :has_dynamic_branding %>
		<%= f.label :has_dynamic_branding, "Has dynamic branding" %><br />
	</p>
	
	